race.comment: PARABELLUM (9) finished a close-up fifth over 2400m at Hanging Rock on January 1. Back in trip and will find this more to her liking. Go close. SATASHI (10) jumped in trip when a fading tenth over 1800m at Gundagai. Comes back a level and proven at the mile. PERFECTLY GOOD (3) settled well back last time out before catching the eye when fifth over 1400m at Gundagai. Outsprinted in the run home but kept coming and looks suited by the extra ground. Among the chances. INCANTATA (11) was far from disgraced when fourth over 1600m at Parkes. That followed a win at Queanbeyan the start prior. Nicely placed to figure in the finish.
